<text top="177" left="90" width="9" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="177" left="126" width="333" height="17" font="3">The General Assembly has thus concluded its </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="371" height="17" font="3">consideration of the fourth report of the General </text>
